Class TitleEvaluationRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.winter.datafusion.EvaluationRule<Movie,Attribute>
      • de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.winter.usecase.movies.datafusion.evaluation.TitleEvaluationRule

  • public class TitleEvaluationRule
extends EvaluationRule<Movie,Attribute>
    EvaluationRule for the titles of Movies. The rule simply compares the titles of two Movies and returns true, in case their similarity based on TokenizingJaccardSimilarity is 1.0.
    Author:
    Oliver Lehmberg (oli@dwslab.de)
